VRClip is a fork of Seal (https://github.com/JunkFood02/Seal) by JunkFood02 and
contributors, licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0. This fork adds:

  - Meta Quest (2, 3, Pro) support, including a fully immersive Meta Spatial SDK
